item.title: Aspose.GIS for .NET 20.04 Release Notes
item.description: This page contains release notes information for Aspose.GIS for .NET 20.04. Major Features Raster features: Read EsriASCII, GeoTIFF and TIFF. Read georeference and raster sizes. Read values of numeric types (Bit, SByte, Byte, Short, UShort, Integer, UInteger, Long, Float, Double). Read raw bits for unknown data types. Read raster data by blocks. Support multy и single bands.
